Packages
Package
Description
ehextractor
Contains the analyzer and high-level classes responsible for extracting 32-bit exception handling information from programs compiled by the Microsoft Visual C++ compiler, finding functions, logging and checking if a binary can be handled by EHExtractor.
instructionpattrns
Contains classes for instruction patterns as implemented by EHExtractor, providing functionality for matching instruction patterns with actual instructions.
loggingbridge
Contains a custom log handler that directs log output to the Ghidra script console.
msvc.exceptions
Contains classes related to the 32-bit exception handling data structures created by Microsoft Visual C++.
msvc.exceptions.code
Contains helper classes for finding function prologues matching how Microsoft Visual C++ (MSVC) creates these when exception handling (EH) is in play, and for matching code that registers the MSVC EH entry data structure (with optional security cookie-checking code before that).
